@startuml clustering_workflow_sequence
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
skinparam maxMessageSize 200

title Flusso Completo Clustering - Quality Threshold Algorithm

actor Utente
participant "ClusteringController\n(GUI)" as Controller
participant "ClusteringService\n(Service Layer)" as Service
participant "JavaFX Task\n(Background Thread)" as Task
participant "Socket\nClient" as Client
participant "ServerOneClient\n(Server Thread)" as Server
participant "QTMiner\n(Algorithm)" as Miner
participant "Data\n(Dataset)" as Data
participant "ClusterSet\n(Result)" as ClusterSet

== Configurazione Clustering ==

Utente -> Controller: Imposta radius e avvia clustering
activate Controller

Controller -> Service: startClustering(config)
activate Service

Service -> Task: new Task<ClusteringResult>()
activate Task

note right of Task
  Esecuzione in background
  per non bloccare UI
end note

Service --> Controller: Task handle
Controller -> Task: setOnSucceeded(handler)
Controller -> Task: ExecutorService.submit(task)

== Connessione Server ==

Task -> Client: new Socket(host, port)
activate Client

Client -> Server: accept() + ObjectStreams
activate Server

note right of Server
  Nuovo thread dedicato
  per questo client
end note

== Scelta Sorgente Dati ==

alt Clustering da Database

    Task -> Client: writeObject(0) // Comando DB
    Client -> Server: readObject() → comando=0

    Task -> Client: writeObject(tableName)
    Client -> Server: readObject() → tableName

    Server -> Data: new Data(tableName)
    activate Data
    Data -> Data: loadFromDatabase()
    Data --> Server: dataset caricato
    deactivate Data

    Server -> Client: writeObject("OK")
    Client -> Task: readObject() → "OK"

    Task -> Client: writeObject(1) // Comando clustering
    Client -> Server: readObject() → comando=1

    Task -> Client: writeObject(radius)
    Client -> Server: readObject() → radius

else Clustering da File

    Task -> Client: writeObject(3) // Comando File
    Client -> Server: readObject() → comando=3

    Task -> Client: writeObject(radius)
    Client -> Server: readObject() → radius

    Task -> Client: writeObject(filePath)
    Client -> Server: readObject() → filePath

    Server -> Data: new Data(filePath)
    activate Data
    Data -> Data: loadFromCSV()
    Data --> Server: dataset caricato
    deactivate Data

end

== Esecuzione Algoritmo QT ==

Server -> Miner: new QTMiner(radius)
activate Miner

Server -> Miner: compute(data)

note right of Miner
  Algoritmo Quality Threshold

  Loop fino a tutte tuple clusterizzate:
  1. buildCandidateCluster()
  2. Trova cluster più grande
  3. Rimuovi tuple clusterizzate

  Complessità: O(k × n²)
end note

loop Per ogni iterazione clustering

    Miner -> Miner: buildCandidateCluster()

    loop Per ogni tupla non clusterizzata
        Miner -> Data: getItemSet(i)
        Data --> Miner: centroid candidate

        loop Per ogni altra tupla
            Miner -> Data: getItemSet(j)
            Data --> Miner: tuple

            Miner -> Miner: centroid.getDistance(tuple)

            alt distance <= radius
                Miner -> Miner: candidateCluster.addData(j)
            end
        end
    end

    Miner -> ClusterSet: add(bestCluster)
    activate ClusterSet
    ClusterSet --> Miner: cluster aggiunto
    deactivate ClusterSet

end

Miner --> Server: numClusters
deactivate Miner

== Restituzione Risultati ==

Server -> ClusterSet: serialize()
activate ClusterSet
ClusterSet --> Server: ClusterSet serializzato
deactivate ClusterSet

Server -> Client: writeObject("OK")
Client -> Task: readObject() → "OK"

Server -> Client: writeObject(clusterSet)
Client -> Task: readObject() → clusterSet

note left of Task
  Deserializzazione
  risultati clustering
end note

Task -> Task: processResults()

== Aggiornamento UI ==

Task -> Controller: onSucceeded()
deactivate Task

Controller -> Controller: updateResultsView()

Controller -> Utente: Mostra risultati
note right of Controller
  - Numero cluster
  - Scatter chart PCA
  - Tabella dettagli
  - Statistiche
end note

deactivate Controller

== Chiusura Connessione ==

Client -> Server: close()
deactivate Server
deactivate Client

note bottom
  Flusso Completo Clustering

  Pattern utilizzati:
  - MVC (Model-View-Controller)
  - Service Layer
  - Background Task (JavaFX)
  - Socket Communication
  - Thread-per-Client (server)

  Gestione errori:
  - IOException → Errore connessione
  - DatabaseConnectionException → DB non disponibile
  - FileNotFoundException → File inesistente
  - Ogni errore propagato come "ERROR: <message>"

  Timeout:
  - Socket read: 30 secondi
  - Task execution: configurabile
end note

@enduml
